lyrics:
[Verse]
Anurag's a poet, sensitive and deep
Words flow through his veins, emotions on repeat
But he's got addictions, a battle he can't win
Food and gambling, his demons from within

[Chorus]
Anurag, oh Anurag, lost among his rhymes
Searching for solace in his vices, every time
Anurag, oh Anurag, can't you break free
From the chains that bind you, let your spirit roam wild and free
